of countries is directly oriented

00:23:08.120 --> 00:23:11.470
only to export or import.

00:23:12.010 --> 00:23:13.950
The main markets that exist

00:23:13.960 --> 00:23:15.830
in the world are exports

00:23:15.840 --> 00:23:17.030
and imports.

00:23:17.040 --> 00:23:20.070
Exports are the exports of goods from the country.

00:23:20.290 --> 00:23:23.290
It is important to note how

00:23:23.550 --> 00:23:25.910
the exports are estimated.

00:23:26.290 --> 00:23:28.970
The value of the export is calculated under

00:23:28.980 --> 00:23:31.590
the so-called FUP price, or the franco-border

00:23:31.600 --> 00:23:33.870
of the country of the exporter.

00:23:33.950 --> 00:23:35.870
That is, it is assumed that the price

00:23:35.880 --> 00:23:38.430
of the export goods includes all the

00:23:38.440 --> 00:23:40.250
costs of its production and transportation

00:23:40.260 --> 00:23:42.390
to the franco-border of

00:23:42.400 --> 00:23:45.350
the country of the exporter.

00:23:45.360 --> 00:23:48.230
As for imports, which involve exports

00:23:48.240 --> 00:23:50.430
of goods from the country, it is

00:23:50.440 --> 00:23:53.070
calculated under the price

00:23:53.080 --> 00:23:58.290
of the SIF, that is, the franco-border

00:23:58.300 --> 00:24:01.050
of the country of the importer.

00:24:01.060 --> 00:24:02.810
Thus, international transportation

00:24:02.820 --> 00:24:07.510
by oceans, by air transport routes,

00:24:07.520 --> 00:24:11.110
these costs are included in the

00:24:11.120 --> 00:24:13.790
price of imported goods.

00:24:13.800 --> 00:24:15.530
That is, only at the time

00:24:15.540 --> 00:24:16.790
of crossing the national

00:24:16.800 --> 00:24:20.530
economic border are fully counted

00:24:20.540 --> 00:24:22.590
those costs that were associated

00:24:22.790 --> 00:24:23.970
with the production

00:24:23.980 --> 00:24:26.030
and transportation of imports.

00:24:27.150 --> 00:24:29.350
I would also like to draw your attention

00:24:29.360 --> 00:24:31.610
to the fact that the volume of exports

00:24:31.620 --> 00:24:34.390
includes not only goods that are

00:24:34.400 --> 00:24:37.970
taken out of the country, but

00:24:37.980 --> 00:24:39.650
also goods for re-export.

00:24:39.660 --> 00:24:40.910
What does this mean?

00:24:41.030 --> 00:24:42.710
When international exhibitions

00:24:42.720 --> 00:24:45.650
are organized, the samples

00:24:45.660 --> 00:24:47.250
presented at these exhibitions

00:24:47.260 --> 00:24:48.910
willingly cross the border,

00:24:48.920 --> 00:24:52.030
for a while are in the so-

00:24:52.040 --> 00:24:54.050
called country of

00:24:54.060 --> 00:24:56.850
the importer, and then return.

00:24:57.490 --> 00:25:04.090
This volume of re-export is also included

00:25:04.100 --> 00:25:06.470
in the volume of exports.

00:25:09.070 --> 00:25:12.950
In general, in the case of international

00:25:12.960 --> 00:25:14.610
division of labor and international

00:25:14.620 --> 00:25:17.730
cooperation, if, for example,

00:25:17.740 --> 00:25:19.410
