00:25:29.820 --> 00:25:31.910
are incorporated into the

00:25:32.490 --> 00:25:35.930
products of domestic

00:25:35.940 --> 00:25:37.350
production.

00:25:37.770 --> 00:25:39.290
After such a substantial processing,

00:25:39.300 --> 00:25:42.290
it is exported back to foreign

00:25:42.300 --> 00:25:43.390
countries.

00:25:43.590 --> 00:25:46.570
It is also a re-export option, but it

00:25:46.580 --> 00:25:48.550
is associated with substantial recycling.

00:25:49.010 --> 00:25:51.110
An important question in the characterization

00:25:51.120 --> 00:25:52.330
of international economic relations

00:25:52.340 --> 00:25:53.690
of the world economy is the indicator

00:25:53.700 --> 00:25:55.250
of the development of foreign

00:25:55.260 --> 00:25:56.570
trade of the country.

00:25:58.410 --> 00:26:01.210
And the most common indicators

00:26:01.220 --> 00:26:02.950
