00:43:31.510 --> 00:43:32.900
must put together the value

00:43:32.910 --> 00:43:35.120
of export and the value

00:43:35.130 --> 00:43:36.000
of import.

00:43:36.120 --> 00:43:37.280
In other words, trade conditions

00:43:37.290 --> 00:43:40.120
are the relationship to

00:43:40.130 --> 00:43:42.400
