00:44:13.450 --> 00:44:15.860
decrease significantly.

00:44:16.020 --> 00:44:18.240
At the same time, the real prices of

00:44:18.250 --> 00:44:20.080
imports seem to have not changed,

00:44:20.090 --> 00:44:21.640
but the relative price expressed

00:44:21.650 --> 00:44:23.520
in trade conditions is changing.

00:44:23.960 --> 00:44:26.580
In this case, the trade condition is

00:44:26.590 --> 00:44:28.640
a more natural indicator, not associated

00:44:28.650 --> 00:44:30.920
with sharp fluctuations in the exchange

00:44:30.930 --> 00:44:32.780
rate, because the trade condition

00:44:32.900 --> 00:44:35.180
can be expressed on the basis

00:44:35.190 --> 00:44:38.620
of such commodity groups,

00:44:38.630 --> 00:44:41.160
so to speak, in currency

00:44:41.170 --> 00:44:44.560
by the peritoneum of purchasing power.

