purchases excess supply to itself.

00:45:11.780 --> 00:45:14.020
But that doesn’t mean that

00:45:14.030 --> 00:45:16.520
there are goods on the domestic market

00:45:16.820 --> 00:45:17.900
that no one needs.

00:45:18.020 --> 00:45:19.560
And this excess offer suddenly

00:45:19.570 --> 00:45:20.980
