00:47:02.910 --> 00:47:05.760
be tolerated to some level.

00:47:05.900 --> 00:47:07.320
Because if this is a long-term

00:47:07.330 --> 00:47:09.340
trend, then, as you know, if

00:47:09.350 --> 00:47:11.100
we buy a lot on imports, but

00:47:11.110 --> 00:47:12.720
at the same time we do not

00:47:12.730 --> 00:47:14.760
pay by exports, and exports

00:47:14.770 --> 00:47:16.280
are shortened, then it means

00:47:16.290 --> 00:47:18.280
that we are in debt, and we

00:47:18.290 --> 00:47:19.900
have to borrow and borrow

00:47:19.910 --> 00:47:21.520
to buy the same amount

00:47:21.530 --> 00:47:25.080
of imports that we want to buy.

00:47:26.940 --> 00:47:29.360
The principle of trade

00:47:29.370 --> 00:47:30.540
balance is this.

00:47:30.600 --> 00:47:31.980
Any restriction on imports

00:47:31.990 --> 00:47:33.100
ultimately leads to restriction

00:47:33.110 --> 00:47:34.180
