00:47:34.260 --> 00:47:36.320
From this, probably, the

00:47:36.330 --> 00:47:37.960
second best principle is when liberalization

00:47:38.100 --> 00:47:40.020
and international

00:47:40.030 --> 00:47:41.680
trade are not bound by any

00:47:41.690 --> 00:47:44.460
restrictions preferably

00:47:44.470 --> 00:47:46.320
than international trade within

00:47:46.330 --> 00:47:48.780
certain restrictions.

00:47:48.880 --> 00:47:50.640
Because, in this case, such international

00:47:50.650 --> 00:47:52.480
competition allows the national

00:47:52.490 --> 00:47:54.380
and world market to supply

00:47:54.390 --> 00:47:56.320
the products that are

00:47:56.330 --> 00:47:58.740
produced with the most effective

00:47:58.750 --> 00:48:02.040
techniques and with the

00:48:02.050 --> 00:48:03.640
most rational use

00:48:03.650 --> 00:48:06.020
of production factors.

00:48:08.940 --> 00:48:12.660
International exchange is still

00:48:12.670 --> 00:48:16.080
strongly linked to the international

00:48:16.090 --> 00:48:17.580
mobility of production

00:48:17.590 --> 00:48:18.680
factors.

