00:48:28.720 --> 00:48:30.440
cities, villages, agricultural

00:48:30.800 --> 00:48:32.740
areas, we can say that in the

00:48:33.160 --> 00:48:34.960
ideal is the absolute mobility

00:48:34.970 --> 00:48:37.280
