00:50:15.010 --> 00:50:16.680
only to the territory of

00:50:16.690 --> 00:50:18.460
the national economy, or these

00:50:18.840 --> 00:50:20.700
factors are mobile allow to

00:50:20.710 --> 00:50:23.480
create these goods on any

00:50:23.490 --> 00:50:24.300
territory.

00:50:24.380 --> 00:50:26.360
There are two categories

00:50:26.370 --> 00:50:29.260
of goods: traded and non-traded.

00:50:29.540 --> 00:50:32.360
In the end, traded goods are easily

00:50:32.370 --> 00:50:34.000
moved between countries,

00:50:34.010 --> 00:50:38.420
thanks to commodity relations.

00:50:39.440 --> 00:50:42.280
And it is assumed that just if some

00:50:42.290 --> 00:50:43.980
factors of production are not mobile,

00:50:43.990 --> 00:50:46.320
they are replaced by exports

00:50:46.330 --> 00:50:48.120
or imports of goods.

