If some factors are mobile, then

00:50:50.610 --> 00:50:52.000
in principle, this production

00:50:52.010 --> 00:50:54.000
can be organized abroad.

00:50:54.460 --> 00:50:56.940
Non-commercial goods are

00:50:56.950 --> 00:50:59.160
consumed only in the country where

00:50:59.260 --> 00:51:00.580
they are produced.

00:51:01.980 --> 00:51:04.600
And in this case, examples of non-

00:51:04.610 --> 00:51:07.020
trade goods are primarily related to the

00:51:07.030 --> 00:51:10.600
country’s infrastructure, with a number

00:51:10.610 --> 00:51:11.680
of services.

00:51:12.040 --> 00:51:13.860
Non-trade means not participating

00:51:13.870 --> 00:51:15.200
in international

00:51:15.210 --> 00:51:16.180
exchange.

00:51:16.190 --> 00:51:18.060
This does not mean that they

00:51:18.070 --> 00:51:21.000
are not in demand, but they

00:51:21.010 --> 00:51:24.960
are limited by their special quality

00:51:24.970 --> 00:51:26.640
of domestic demand and

00:51:26.650 --> 00:51:28.680
therefore sold only in national

00:51:28.690 --> 00:51:30.000
territories.

00:51:30.000 --> 00:51:32.770
Accordingly, the price of trade goods

00:51:32.780 --> 00:51:35.570
is determined based on domestic

00:51:35.580 --> 00:51:37.450
