00:51:37.460 --> 00:51:39.630
according to the system that

00:51:39.640 --> 00:51:41.110
we have already considered

00:51:41.120 --> 00:51:42.430
when establishing the world

00:51:42.440 --> 00:51:43.490
price.

00:51:43.890 --> 00:51:46.350
But the prices of non-commercial

00:51:46.360 --> 00:51:49.630
