to conclude an agreement

03:06:21.600 --> 03:06:23.190
between the Academy of

03:06:23.200 --> 03:06:24.870
Sciences and universities.

03:06:24.910 --> 03:06:28.170
That is, there is training of personnel

03:06:28.180 --> 03:06:29.970
and specialists, such an international

03:06:29.980 --> 03:06:31.950
exchange, within which transfer,

03:06:31.960 --> 03:06:34.690
international transfer of technology

03:06:34.700 --> 03:06:36.410
is also possible.

