First, within the framework of modern

03:36:14.650 --> 03:36:16.540
liberalization processes,

03:36:16.550 --> 03:36:21.140
the scope of instruments regulating

03:36:21.150 --> 03:36:23.120
mechanisms of foreign trade

03:36:23.130 --> 03:36:25.060
relations is expanding.

03:36:25.620 --> 03:36:27.780
In addition to tariffs, various

03:36:27.790 --> 03:36:30.140
forms of financial support

