03:38:10.070 --> 03:38:14.800
to the fact that if countries

03:38:14.810 --> 03:38:19.060
that have joined in an integration

03:38:19.070 --> 03:38:21.240
union to develop international

03:38:21.250 --> 03:38:23.700
economic relations, switch

