Of course, getting on such a blacklist

04:15:53.170 --> 04:15:59.680
is not a good option for

04:16:00.080 --> 04:16:02.460
those countries in transition that

04:16:02.470 --> 04:16:05.820
are developing their exports

04:16:05.830 --> 04:16:07.420
and imports.

