countries, they try to regulate,

05:09:13.270 --> 05:09:16.210
order currency-financial relations

05:09:16.290 --> 05:09:18.630
between the countries that

05:09:18.640 --> 05:09:21.190
are members of the International

05:09:21.200 --> 05:09:23.350
Monetary Fund.

05:09:23.510 --> 05:09:25.370
The next component of the currency

05:09:25.380 --> 05:09:27.850
system is currency parity.

05:09:28.310 --> 05:09:29.110
What is this?

05:09:29.230 --> 05:09:30.930
This is the ratio of the value of two

05:09:30.940 --> 05:09:33.610
currencies expressed through the third means.

05:09:33.620 --> 05:09:35.950
This is a kind of basis that

05:09:35.960 --> 05:09:41.510
allows the central bank to identify

05:09:41.520 --> 05:09:44.190
the average component around

05:09:44.210 --> 05:09:46.510
which the exchange rate will

05:09:46.520 --> 05:09:49.510
eventually fluctuate.

05:09:49.520 --> 05:09:54.830
What is the basis on which

05:09:54.840 --> 05:09:57.270
currency parity is calculated?

05:09:57.710 --> 05:09:59.470
These are global reserves.

05:10:00.150 --> 05:10:02.130
In ancient times, gold and

05:10:02.140 --> 05:10:03.950
silver were such reserves.

05:10:04.730 --> 05:10:07.430
At present, gold has retained its reserve

05:10:07.440 --> 05:10:09.530
function, despite the fact that

05:10:09.540 --> 05:10:12.770
gold has ceased to be a means of

05:10:12.780 --> 05:10:14.630
exchange or payment, there are no

05:10:14.640 --> 05:10:16.810
gold coins, but nevertheless all the

05:10:16.820 --> 05:10:19.530
central banks of the world hold

05:10:19.540 --> 05:10:21.830
in their gold reserves gold,

05:10:21.840 --> 05:10:26.630
as that value that can be the means

05:10:26.640 --> 05:10:29.430
of final settlements between countries

05:10:29.440 --> 05:10:31.250
in the negative trade balance

05:10:31.260 --> 05:10:34.130
and falling rates of national

05:10:34.140 --> 05:10:37.570
and foreign currencies,

05:10:37.580 --> 05:10:39.110
that is, in the financial

05:10:39.120 --> 05:10:40.730
crisis.

05:10:41.210 --> 05:10:43.310
If we recall the situation of the

05:10:44.880 --> 05:10:47.750
70s, when the currency and financial crisis

05:10:47.760 --> 05:10:50.530
occurred, then as we remember, at

05:10:50.540 --> 05:10:53.050
this time the collapse of the Bratenwood

05:10:53.060 --> 05:10:54.390
system occurred.

05:10:54.410 --> 05:10:58.210
The system in which the US dollar was

05:10:58.220 --> 05:11:00.110
calculated on the currency parity

05:11:00.120 --> 05:11:01.910
to gold, that is, had gold content,

05:11:01.920 --> 05:11:04.690
and all the leading countries in the

05:11:04.700 --> 05:11:06.170
world equated their currencies

05:11:06.180 --> 05:11:07.710
to the dollar, and in relation

05:11:07.720 --> 05:11:11.650
to it calculated the value content

05:11:11.660 --> 05:11:13.190
of their currency.

05:11:13.200 --> 05:11:14.690
So at this time, when in the 1970s

05:11:14.870 --> 05:11:18.110
Europe was over-saturated with euros

05:11:18.120 --> 05:11:20.250
and dollars, the central banks

05:11:20.810 --> 05:11:23.350
of the future European Union

05:11:23.360 --> 05:11:26.910
practically bought dollars to

05:11:26.920 --> 05:11:30.390
then exchange them in the central

05:11:30.400 --> 05:11:32.990
bank of the United States for

05:11:33.000 --> 05:11:34.110
gold.

05:11:34.330 --> 05:11:35.990
And during this period of time,

05:11:36.000 --> 05:11:38.870
the US spent 50% of its gold

05:11:38.880 --> 05:11:40.590
reserves to restore the

05:11:40.600 --> 05:11:42.210
financial system.

05:11:42.220 --> 05:11:45.430
In order to prevent this from happening

05:11:45.440 --> 05:11:47.710
again, the International Monetary

05:11:47.720 --> 05:11:50.450
Fund created special borrowing

05:11:50.460 --> 05:11:51.830
rights, i.e. a system in which

05:11:51.840 --> 05:11:54.210
the world’s leading countries,

05:11:54.220 --> 05:11:55.970
members of the International Monetary

05:11:55.980 --> 05:11:59.350
Fund, invested solid currencies

05:11:59.360 --> 05:12:01.630
in the International Monetary

05:12:01.640 --> 05:12:03.390
Fund, in particular Russia,

05:12:03.400 --> 05:12:04.790
when joining the International

05:12:04.800 --> 05:12:07.950
Monetary Fund, offered gold

05:12:07.960 --> 05:12:10.210
as reserves, since at that

05:12:10.220 --> 05:12:13.250
time it did not have convertible

05:12:13.260 --> 05:12:15.550
currencies to provide

05:12:15.560 --> 05:12:17.290
such reserves.

05:12:17.350 --> 05:12:20.270
What is the SDR Special Borrowing Rights?

05:12:20.350 --> 05:12:23.330
In fact, they are sometimes called paper

05:12:23.340 --> 05:12:25.290
money, that is, it is some securities,

05:12:25.300 --> 05:12:27.230
it is virtual securities, it is

05:12:27.240 --> 05:12:29.210
a record on the accounts of the

05:12:29.220 --> 05:12:31.350
International Monetary Fund and a

05:12:31.360 --> 05:12:34.370
corrected record on the accounts of

05:12:34.380 --> 05:12:36.830
the central banks of countries.

05:12:37.110 --> 05:12:39.690
But it is considered

05:12:39.700 --> 05:12:41.710
the most convertible currency,

05:12:41.720 --> 05:12:44.030
and in this case countries can

05:12:44.040 --> 05:12:46.030
pay for just these securities

05:12:46.040 --> 05:12:48.350
with special borrowing rights.

05:12:48.430 --> 05:12:50.130
Basically, of course, they are

05:12:50.140 --> 05:12:52.410
not rejected, kept and probably

05:12:52.530 --> 05:12:54.310
resorted to them at the last moment.

05:12:56.590 --> 05:13:00.710
What else is in the world reserves?

05:13:01.050 --> 05:13:03.290
This is a foreign currency, another

05:13:03.300 --> 05:13:04.830
name is a currency.

05:13:05.270 --> 05:13:07.310
I will return to this issue later.

05:13:07.320 --> 05:13:09.190
Now the second point that could still

05:13:09.200 --> 05:13:12.410
be included in the calculation of parity.

05:13:12.930 --> 05:13:15.910
There is also a variant of such a calculated

05:13:15.920 --> 05:13:19.150
parity of the exchange rate, when

05:13:19.160 --> 05:13:21.690
exchange rates are compared on the

05:13:21.700 --> 05:13:23.690
basket, on purchasing power,

05:13:23.700 --> 05:13:28.090
the possibility to buy goods in one

05:13:28.100 --> 05:13:29.890
country and in another country for

05:13:29.900 --> 05:13:31.830
their currency and for foreign

05:13:31.840 --> 05:13:33.230
currency.

05:13:33.240 --> 05:13:35.250
The parity of purchasing

05:13:35.260 --> 05:13:38.170
power implies a calculated

05:13:38.180 --> 05:13:40.190
exchange rate, which is

05:13:40.250 --> 05:13:42.210
called a real exchange rate.

05:13:42.220 --> 05:13:42.490
Why is?

05:13:42.570 --> 05:13:44.490
Because it takes into account the level

05:13:44.500 --> 05:13:47.090
of inflation in foreign countries and

05:13:47.100 --> 05:13:48.710
in the home country.

05:13:48.810 --> 05:13:50.290
Thus, most clearly, unlike

05:13:50.300 --> 05:13:51.990
the market exchange rate,

05:13:52.000 --> 05:13:53.710
which is influenced by demand

05:13:53.720 --> 05:13:55.770
and supply, shows the real

05:13:55.780 --> 05:13:58.150
purchasing power of a country.

05:13:58.310 --> 05:13:59.570
In particular, by the parity

05:13:59.580 --> 05:14:01.410
of purchasing power, the exchange

05:14:01.420 --> 05:14:03.970
rate of Russia should be not about

05:14:03.980 --> 05:14:07.030
25 rubles per dollar, but only

05:14:07.040 --> 05:14:07.870
15.

05:14:08.130 --> 05:14:10.310
That is, purchasing power is

05:14:10.320 --> 05:14:12.210
strong enough because we have

05:14:12.290 --> 05:14:13.630
a fairly high export,

05:14:13.640 --> 05:14:15.750
although, in general, recently

05:14:15.760 --> 05:14:17.910
and high imports.

05:14:19.870 --> 05:14:21.730
Purchasing power parity is calculated

05:14:21.740 --> 05:14:24.890
by different methods.

05:14:24.900 --> 05:14:27.450
As I said, you can count through

05:14:27.470 --> 05:14:30.610
comparable baskets of goods.

05:14:30.620 --> 05:14:32.870
It is clear that these should

05:14:32.880 --> 05:14:34.570
not be goods of local consumption

05:14:34.580 --> 05:14:36.530
that are not related to

05:14:36.540 --> 05:14:40.290
international preferences.

05:14:40.590 --> 05:14:42.330
This is the product that

05:14:42.450 --> 05:14:45.190
is consumed in any country.

05:14:45.310 --> 05:14:47.790
And the simplest example is the

05:14:47.800 --> 05:14:50.030
establishment of parity for

05:14:50.040 --> 05:14:52.550
a single product, which is distributed

05:14:52.560 --> 05:14:54.010
all over the world.

05:14:54.030 --> 05:14:56.110
In this regard, McDonald’s can be

05:14:56.120 --> 05:14:57.830
proud that one of the options for calculating

05:14:57.840 --> 05:14:59.410
the purchasing power parity –

05:14:59.420 --> 05:15:00.890
though, the most approximate –

05:15:00.900 --> 05:15:03.170
is the ratio of prices to hamburgers

05:15:03.180 --> 05:15:04.730
in different countries.

05:15:04.810 --> 05:15:06.530
Depending on the price ratio,

05:15:06.540 --> 05:15:09.490
you can calculate the most

05:15:09.500 --> 05:15:14.390
correct, more adequate exchange

05:15:14.400 --> 05:15:16.150
rate or real exchange

05:15:16.160 --> 05:15:17.210
rate.

05:15:17.330 --> 05:15:19.330
In statistics, the central

05:15:19.370 --> 05:15:20.810
bank calculates the parity

05:15:20.820 --> 05:15:25.210
of the purchasing power of a currency

05:15:25.220 --> 05:15:28.110
by more complex methods, as

05:15:28.120 --> 05:15:29.670
I said, through price

05:15:29.680 --> 05:15:30.610
indices.

05:15:30.810 --> 05:15:34.150
This is due to the changes in

05:15:34.160 --> 05:15:38.530
inflation in the country and

05:15:38.540 --> 05:15:40.070
abroad.

05:15:40.750 --> 05:15:42.890
The next component of the currency

05:15:42.900 --> 05:15:44.710
system is the currency standard.

05:15:45.550 --> 05:15:46.270
What is it?

05:15:46.290 --> 05:15:49.010
This is a currency parity system.

05:15:49.690 --> 05:15:51.530
That is, every country, every

05:15:51.540 --> 05:15:58.490
government, the central bank or what

05:15:58.500 --> 05:16:00.330
will eventually lie in the same reserves

05:16:00.340 --> 05:16:03.950
of the country as in the case

05:16:03.960 --> 05:16:07.370
of calculations, which

05:16:07.380 --> 05:16:10.290
reserves will have to be abandoned.

05:16:11.170 --> 05:16:13.230
The oldest standard was the

05:16:13.240 --> 05:16:14.870
metal standard, that is, the

05:16:14.880 --> 05:16:17.910
same gold, silver and so on.

05:16:18.070 --> 05:16:20.450
In principle, the gold standard was

05:16:20.460 --> 05:16:24.250
introduced in the 20th century twice, this

05:16:24.260 --> 05:16:26.710
was in the pre-war period, and some

05:16:26.720 --> 05:16:28.430
short time in a number of countries after

05:16:28.440 --> 05:16:30.730
the war, but eventually it was abandoned.

05:16:31.250 --> 05:16:34.190
Even after the 1970s crisis, the

05:16:34.290 --> 05:16:35.670
currency and financial crisis,

05:16:35.790 --> 05:16:37.830
gold was said to have ceased

05:16:37.840 --> 05:16:40.550
to be the world’s most valuable money

05:16:40.560 --> 05:16:42.090
and means of payment, because

05:16:42.100 --> 05:16:44.030
it has low liquidity.

05:16:44.350 --> 05:16:46.590
But the metal standard

05:16:46.600 --> 05:16:48.890
has remained to some extent.

05:16:48.930 --> 05:16:49.270
Why is?

05:16:49.370 --> 05:16:50.790
Because it is now included

05:16:50.800 --> 05:16:51.770
in a more modern type

05:16:51.780 --> 05:16:53.090
of gold standard.

05:16:53.110 --> 05:16:55.590
What is the Division Standard,

05:16:55.710 --> 05:16:56.930
the Modern Standard?

05:16:57.050 --> 05:17:01.230
In this case, the currency is

05:17:01.240 --> 05:17:05.670
selected in relation to some currencies.

05:17:05.680 --> 05:17:07.690
You can choose a currency parity in

05:17:07.700 --> 05:17:09.490
relation to one currency, you can

05:17:09.500 --> 05:17:11.550
in relation to a basket of currencies,

05:17:11.560 --> 05:17:12.890
you can only special borrowing

05:17:12.900 --> 05:17:14.870
rights, you can gold currency,

05:17:14.880 --> 05:17:16.290
special borrowing rights,

05:17:16.300 --> 05:17:17.690
and so on.

05:17:19.290 --> 05:17:21.330
If you pay attention to the

05:17:21.340 --> 05:17:23.010
state of gold and foreign exchange reserves

05:17:23.020 --> 05:17:27.570
in Russia and look at what solid

05:17:27.580 --> 05:17:30.410
currencies they consist of, then until

05:17:31.980 --> 05:17:34.490
recently the main reserve

05:17:34.500 --> 05:17:36.610
currency, in addition to

05:17:36.620 --> 05:17:38.610
special borrowing rights and gold,

05:17:38.620 --> 05:17:40.050
was the dollar.

05:17:40.060 --> 05:17:43.190
However, such a dependence on the dollar

05:17:43.200 --> 05:17:46.430
in the situation of instability

05:17:46.440 --> 05:17:49.310
and various political fluctuations

05:17:49.320 --> 05:17:51.010
in the United States is quite

05:17:51.020 --> 05:17:54.990
dangerous for any currency

05:17:55.000 --> 05:17:56.750
system.

05:17:57.050 --> 05:17:59.770
Accordingly, as soon as the opportunity

05:17:59.780 --> 05:18:03.030
arose to replenish the country's

05:18:03.040 --> 05:18:06.230
reserves with a solid European

05:18:06.240 --> 05:18:08.210
currency, European currencies

05:18:08.220 --> 05:18:14.570
began to be included.

05:18:14.580 --> 05:18:17.370
In the current conditions, when

05:18:17.380 --> 05:18:20.030
the euro area was formed, the currency

05:18:20.040 --> 05:18:24.510
component is 45% of the dollar and

05:18:24.520 --> 05:18:30.370
the euro, and 10% relates to the

05:18:30.380 --> 05:18:32.870
pound sterling as a fairly

05:18:32.880 --> 05:18:35.050
solid and stable currency.

05:18:35.060 --> 05:18:37.410
In principle, if you look at the

05:18:37.420 --> 05:18:40.610
value of gold and currency reserves,

05:18:40.850 --> 05:18:44.750
then in fact the value of the euro is 60%

05:18:44.760 --> 05:18:48.630
of our currency reserves, and accordingly

05:18:48.640 --> 05:18:51.470
the value of the dollar is much

05:18:51.480 --> 05:18:53.590
lower.

05:18:54.390 --> 05:18:57.530
The supplementation of our gold and currency

05:18:57.540 --> 05:19:00.510
reserves may be the flow of Japanese yen.

05:19:00.520 --> 05:19:03.370
This was announced in October

05:19:03.380 --> 05:19:06.690
2006 and the Japanese Finance

05:19:06.700 --> 05:19:09.610
Minister noted with satisfaction

05:19:09.620 --> 05:19:12.130
such a trend in Russian

05:19:12.140 --> 05:19:15.510
financial and monetary policy.

05:19:16.210 --> 05:19:18.230
But the exact content of the Japanese

05:19:18.240 --> 05:19:19.810
yen in the currency component

05:19:19.820 --> 05:19:23.590
is not announced.

05:19:23.600 --> 05:19:25.450
Well, apparently, just that 10% along

05:19:25.460 --> 05:19:28.010
with the pound sterling may

05:19:28.020 --> 05:19:30.350
and will be held by the Japanese

05:19:30.360 --> 05:19:31.430
yen.

05:19:31.850 --> 05:19:34.050
However, it is said that, given

05:19:36.480 --> 05:19:40.910
that the factory of the world and

05:19:40.920 --> 05:19:44.110
the main export partner of many

05:19:44.120 --> 05:19:46.370
countries in the world is China, some

05:19:47.050 --> 05:19:50.530
countries are thinking about including

05:19:50.540 --> 05:19:53.710
the Chinese currency yuan in the

05:19:53.720 --> 05:19:56.350
currency component of their

05:19:56.360 --> 05:19:56.990
countries.

05:19:57.290 --> 05:19:59.930
But this decision has not yet been made.

05:20:03.140 --> 05:20:05.660
The next component of the currency

05:20:05.670 --> 05:20:07.420
system is the currency regime.

05:20:09.180 --> 05:20:13.120
And depending on how developed a

05:20:13.130 --> 05:20:15.020
country is, or so to say,

05:20:15.030 --> 05:20:17.200
developing, what types of domestic

05:20:17.210 --> 05:20:18.900
economic policy it conducts, one

05:20:18.910 --> 05:20:21.460
or the other country adheres to

05:20:21.470 --> 05:20:25.340
different options of flexibility

05:20:25.350 --> 05:20:27.460
of the exchange rate.

05:20:28.100 --> 05:20:30.000
At least we can look

05:20:30.010 --> 05:20:32.480
at the slide.

05:20:32.500 --> 05:20:35.680
There are three flexibility options.

05:20:35.800 --> 05:20:37.360
The most extreme option is a tightly

05:20:37.370 --> 05:20:39.320
fixed exchange rate.

05:20:39.700 --> 05:20:42.780
Another opposite side of currency

05:20:42.790 --> 05:20:44.660
flexibility is the freely floating

05:20:44.670 --> 05:20:46.060
exchange rate.

05:20:46.070 --> 05:20:48.060
This is perfect swimming.

05:20:48.440 --> 05:20:50.300
And in the meantime, regulated

05:20:50.310 --> 05:20:52.600
swimming, which was just in the 70s received

05:20:52.610 --> 05:20:55.020
the term "dirty swimming", that

05:20:55.030 --> 05:20:56.340
is, swimming, related to the state

05:20:56.420 --> 05:20:57.680
interventions of the Central

05:20:57.690 --> 05:20:59.560
Bank on the currency market with

05:20:59.570 --> 05:21:01.660
the purchase of the sale of currency

05:21:01.670 --> 05:21:02.880
and, accordingly, the maintenance

05:21:03.060 --> 05:21:05.220
of one or another degree of

05:21:05.230 --> 05:21:06.820
its domestic currency.

05:21:12.340 --> 05:21:13.920
A hardly fixed exchange rate,

05:21:13.930 --> 05:21:17.880
although it seems that

05:21:17.890 --> 05:21:19.340
in the modern world countries

05:21:19.350 --> 05:21:21.800
should abandon it, yet it has

05:21:21.810 --> 05:21:23.020
certain advantages,

05:21:23.030 --> 05:21:24.640
which we will talk about

05:21:24.650 --> 05:21:25.740
later.

05:21:27.220 --> 05:21:28.580
In particular, for example, China

05:21:28.800 --> 05:21:31.880
has a tightly fixed exchange rate,

05:21:31.890 --> 05:21:34.380
which allows to reduce the exchange

05:21:34.390 --> 05:21:37.640
rate, the exchange rate of the

05:21:37.650 --> 05:21:40.000
Chinese yuan against the United

05:21:40.010 --> 05:21:41.020
States.

05:21:41.680 --> 05:21:44.020
Although, ideally, as I said, the exchange

05:21:44.200 --> 05:21:45.740
rate should rise, because in terms

05:21:45.750 --> 05:21:47.320
of purchasing power parity

05:21:47.330 --> 05:21:48.740
it is much higher, precisely

05:21:48.750 --> 05:21:51.020
because China is now leading

05:21:51.030 --> 05:21:52.760
in foreign trade, in terms

05:21:52.770 --> 05:21:54.740
of the growth rate of foreign

05:21:54.750 --> 05:21:56.140
trade in the world.

05:22:03.980 --> 05:22:05.720
Variants of the floating exchange

05:22:05.730 --> 05:22:07.380
rate are the adjusted exchange

05:22:07.390 --> 05:22:08.620
rate.

05:22:08.640 --> 05:22:10.980
This is a currency exchange rate that

05:22:10.990 --> 05:22:12.540
automatically changes depending

05:22:12.550 --> 05:22:15.240
on the macroeconomic indicators

05:22:15.250 --> 05:22:16.060
listed in the legislation,

05:22:16.070 --> 05:22:17.640
such as the level of inflation

05:22:17.650 --> 05:22:19.900
or the country’s balance

05:22:19.910 --> 05:22:22.120
of payments.

05:22:23.240 --> 05:22:25.040
The next direction is controlled

05:22:25.050 --> 05:22:26.620
floating and, accordingly,

05:22:26.630 --> 05:22:27.820
controlled floating

05:22:27.830 --> 05:22:29.760
exchange rate.

05:22:30.320 --> 05:22:33.060
How does the state manage

05:22:33.070 --> 05:22:34.900
this floating course?

05:22:34.920 --> 05:22:36.460
These are not automatic changes.

05:22:36.600 --> 05:22:37.660
That is, it is assumed that

05:22:37.670 --> 05:22:39.420
the Central Bank in this case

05:22:39.430 --> 05:22:41.940
decides to change the exchange

05:22:41.950 --> 05:22:43.900
rate by intervening in

05:22:43.910 --> 05:22:46.320
the currency market.

