05:23:11.830 --> 05:23:13.340
exchange rate as perfect competition,

05:23:13.350 --> 05:23:16.160
or a theoretical option.

05:23:16.380 --> 05:23:18.180
No, independently floating exchange

05:23:18.190 --> 05:23:20.100
rates in such a system periodically

05:23:20.110 --> 05:23:22.360
come when they have a crisis

05:23:22.370 --> 05:23:23.920
of the national financial

05:23:23.930 --> 05:23:25.020
system.

