05:31:20.810 --> 05:31:23.900
Bank is trying to change the situation

05:31:23.910 --> 05:31:26.460
on the exchange rate, and the

05:31:26.470 --> 05:31:28.440
process is further stabilized during

05:31:28.450 --> 05:31:31.620
the first quarter of 2006.

05:31:31.840 --> 05:31:34.260
This is precisely due to the fact that

