If the state does not intervene,

05:35:25.700 --> 05:35:27.100
then the excess supply,

05:35:27.110 --> 05:35:28.980
say, of dollars at such a costly

05:35:28.990 --> 05:35:31.560
exchange rate, will eventually lead

05:35:31.570 --> 05:35:33.260
to the fall of demand for the

05:35:33.270 --> 05:35:36.880
